Name: Tokiko{br}

As a flier, Tokiko has amazing utility in being able to be basically anywhere on the map in a quick time, alongside rescuing and ferrying units where they need to be. 
Beyond this, Tokiko's skill "Knowledge is Power" allows you to more efficiently train up weapon exp.

Name: Letty Whiterock{br}Working Hours: December - February{br}
Letty is a very strange character, scaling off of a weird mix of Mag and Res. Her "Flood of Frost" combat art allows her to slow down enemies and boost her own damage at the same time (indirectly through the Res boost). 
Letty does absolutely wonderfully against magic users, but she might flounder a bit if she's caught on the defense against physical units.

Name: Unknown{br}Nickname: Daiyousei{br}
An unexpectedly strong fairy that lives along Misty Lake's shores. A few villagers have mentioned seeing her playing with the others a few times. Her power is anomalously above average for a fairy. Appears to be a sub-leader amongst the fairies. [Reference Needed.] She seems to share a bond with the ice fairy, although the two have been seen by Marisa Kirisame to have come to blows a few times. Fairies are quite fickle. For categorization purposes, I will title her "Daiyousei", as her power is "bigger" than the average fairy.
Daiyousei builds up Crit very fast using her ability, Nature Power. She should be used with high critical weapons to get the most out of her ability to spam critical hits.
